# Lodge & Conference Images
Store all accommodation and conference facility images here.

Suggested organization:
- rooms/ (guest rooms, suites)
- conference/ (meeting rooms, conference halls)
- amenities/ (pool, gym, spa, etc.)
- exterior/ (building exterior, grounds)
- dining/ (restaurant, bar areas)

Image guidelines:
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Resolution: 1920x1080px for hero images, 1200x800px for galleries
- File size: Under 500KB each
- Professional photography recommended
- Use descriptive filenames (e.g., deluxe-suite-bedroom.jpg)